definitions.definition: Zamboanga City (a city in Zamboanga Peninsula , Mindanao , Philippines )
Zamboanga Peninsula (an administrative region of Mindanao , Philippines ).
Zamboanga peninsula (a peninsula in Mindanao , Philippines ).
Province of Zamboanga (a former province of Mindanao , Philippines )
The Republic of Zamboanga , a short-lived revolutionary republic , founded after the collapse of Spanish colonial rule in the Philippines , existing between May and November 1899.
